{"title":"塞外落户","authors":["曾昭安"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞外落户"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾昭安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳下汽车，抓一把土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丢掉泥巴，拔一根草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看它像不像家乡土？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看它像不像家乡草？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻来复去，瞧了又瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它还是和乡土没有两样！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬来咬去，尝了又尝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它还是和乡草一样芳香！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找位老大爷问路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻位老大娘讨碗水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看他像不像故乡人？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尝尝它像不像故乡水？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问来问去，嗓子都哑了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个人都是勤咀笑脸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讨来讨去，肚子都涨了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碗碗水都是明澈清凉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我赶快安排好我的家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用双手挖了一个坑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把来自南国的红豆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同我的心种在这荒野上。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}